# 100 Fantasy Archetypes

## ⚔️ Villains & Antagonists

- **Powerful Villain** — Commanding presence, dark robes, glowing eyes, dramatic lighting
- **Dark Knight** / Armor — Black armored warrior, visor down, sword raised, cinematic fog
- **Dystopian Road Warrior** — Post-apocalyptic gear, desert wasteland, aggressive stance
- **Trickster** — Mischievous grin, colorful costume, playing cards, smoke and mirrors
- **Cunning Rogue** — Hooded figure, daggers drawn, shadowy alleyway
- **Fallen Hero Seeking Redemption** — Battle-worn armor, haunted expression, glowing relic in hand
- **Beastly Creature** — Massive, snarling, fur and muscle, glowing red eyes
- **Necromancer** — Dark robes, skeletal hands raised, swirling purple energy
- **Demon Lord** — Towering horned figure, wings spread, fire and shadow
- **Warlord** — Heavy spiked armor, battlefield backdrop, war banner behind him

---

## 🦸 Heroes & Champions

- **Heroic Warrior** / Cape — Full armor, flowing cape, sword raised, golden hour light
- **Noble King/Queen** — Tribal queen, jeweled armor and crown, full body, holding a dagger
- **Orphan on a Quest** — Young traveler, worn satchel, determined expression, open road ahead
- **Damsel in Distress** — Elegant gown, distressed expression, tower window, moonlight
- **Guardian** / Staff — Ancient warrior in ceremonial armor, glowing staff, stone temple
- **Noble Queen** — Regal gown, crown, throne room, confident pose
- **Female Swordsman** — Athletic build, dual swords, dynamic fighting stance, forest backdrop
- **Femme Fatale** — Full body, perfect silhouette, visible abs, flowing purple cape, smoldering gaze
- **Oversized Muscular Brute** — Enormous build, war hammer, battle-scarred skin, stormy skies
- **Barbarian Nomadic Warrior** — Female barbarian warrior, wearing fur, full body, holding a sword, wild hair
- **Paladin** — Holy armor, divine light, shield with crest, righteous stance
- **Wandering Swordsman** — Lone figure, katana or longsword, misty mountain path
- **Berserker** — Raging warrior, axe mid-swing, battle frenzy, war paint
- **Knight in Shining Armor** — Gleaming plate armor, white horse, castle in background
- **Rebel Princess** — Crown slightly askew, armor under royal dress, defiant expression

